(354,5,'2024-04-26 09:08:40','2024-04-26 09:08:40','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>From his review of my Frontend page:  <a href=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/index.php/your-front-end-development-journey-a-step-by-step-roadmap/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"299\">Your Front-End Development Journey: A Step-by-Step Roadmap</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":353,\"width\":\"690px\",\"height\":\"auto\",\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/work-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-353\" style=\"width:690px;height:auto\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I am a Frontend Web Developer with 5+ years of experience in developing websites. I have a passion for creating user-friendly, visually appealing, and functional websites. My expertise lies in HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript, React js, Tailwind, and Bootstrap. I have a strong understanding of web standards and accessibility guidelines.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Philemon\'s contributions','','inherit','closed','closed','','294-revision-v1','','','2024-04-26 09:08:40','2024-04-26 09:08:40','',294,'https://michaelkentburns.com/?p=354',0,'revision','',0),
(356,5,'2024-04-26 09:11:25','2024-04-26 09:11:25','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>From his review of my Frontend page:  <a href=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/index.php/your-front-end-development-journey-a-step-by-step-roadmap/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"299\">Your Front-End Development Journey: A Step-by-Step Roadmap</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":353,\"width\":\"690px\",\"height\":\"auto\",\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/work-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-353\" style=\"width:690px;height:auto\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hi! My name is Philemon Bahati, I am a Frontend Web Developer with 5+ years of experience in developing websites. I have a passion for creating user-friendly, visually appealing, and functional websites. My expertise lies in HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript, React js, Tailwind, and Bootstrap. I have a strong understanding of web standards and accessibility guidelines.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Philemon\'s contributions','','inherit','closed','closed','','294-revision-v1','','','2024-04-26 09:11:25','2024-04-26 09:11:25','',294,'https://michaelkentburns.com/?p=356',0,'revision','',0),
