(488,1,'2024-06-28 22:38:31','2024-06-28 22:38:31','<!-- wp:group {\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:group {\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:gallery {\"linkTo\":\"none\",\"layout\":{\"type\":\"flex\",\"flexWrap\":null}} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":169,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/MichaelAtWork-1024x768.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-169\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Michael</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":353,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/work-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-353\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Philémon</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></figure>\n<!-- /wp:gallery --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Software development freelancing...</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>There are many locations around the globe that are hotspots for software development.   If you happen to live in one of those places, jobs can come looking for you.   But there are many places around the world that have little or no jobs in this field.  In those places you need some extra skills to get and keep work, but it can be done.  This site is a place to find help and to build community of fellow developers.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Learn a little about me and why I am developing this site on my <a href=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/index.php/about-michael/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"22\">About page...</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">New Content:</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><img class=\"wp-image-420\" style=\"width: 50px;\" src=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/New.jpg\" alt=\"\">  In the sidebar on the left I have added a link to <strong><a href=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/index.php/blog/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"449\">Latest Blog Posts page</a></strong> so you can look there for new posts you may not have read.   Also there is a <a href=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/index.php/chronological-index-of-blog-posts/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"483\"><strong>Cronological Index to Blog Posts</strong></a> that lists all of my blog posts with short excerpts. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Welcome</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>My intention with this main page is to tell a story of a journey that you might be on.  I\'ll try to keep it pretty brief and include \"Learn more...\" links so you can dive deeper as you need.   Hopefully you will find yourself on this journey and find where you are in the story.  When you do, I invite you to contact me.  My intention is that I can help guide you along.   I hope that this will become a community of like minded people.  I invite you to help me understand your needs and together we will keep you moving.  No tricks or fees are involved.   See my <a href=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/index.php/about-michael/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"22\">About page</a> for that background.  If you have questions or comments along the way please <a href=\"mailto: MichaelKentBurns@gmail.com\">email me</a>.   This site is a work in progress and I intend to develop it to meet the needs of my readers. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Developing your skills</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>While traditional full time employment brings a degree of long term job security, freelancers need to keep their current skills fresh in order to stay relevant.  High tech work is constantly changing with new fields opening up almost daily.  Those new fields often have a higher demand for skilled individuals.  Being willing and able to add new skills will increase your chances of finding work and better pay.  </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Front end web</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The World Wide Web is a rapidly evolving place, and it is a challenging field to stay fresh in.   Sometimes there are dramatic shifts in interactive technology.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/index.php/front-end-web/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"49\">Learn more about front end work...</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Back end web</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Back end technologies don\'t change as fast as front end, but...</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/index.php/back-end-web/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"52\">Learn more about back end work...</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Full stack</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>On the surface full stack development is just front end and back end, but there is more to consider...</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/index.php/full-stack/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"55\">Learn more about putting it all together...</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Working globally</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>With the advent of <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open-source_software\"><strong>open-source software</strong></a> there arose the need to have world wide access to the source code for the many projects.   <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Git\"><strong>Git</strong></a> is the source control tool invented for Linux development.  <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/GitHub\"><strong>GitHub</strong></a> is a web interface for software development which uses Git for the source control features, and describes itself as collaborative version control.   It not only allows you to manage your own projects but lets you share them.  Furthermore it lets you explore a vast galaxy of other projects that you can learn from, and in some cases contribute to.  That is a great way of building your reputation. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/?page_id=59\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"59\">Learn more about how software is developed globally...</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Let\'s get acquainted so I can figure out how I can begin to help you. </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Please take the first challenge to tell me about yourself.  Once we get acquainted I can learn about your needs and desires and continue to develop this site to help you move forward.   I can also get some feedback from you on what is helpful and what is not so much.  Eventually, I would like you to consider being more actively involved in making this site a place where you can help others and learn from them too. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/index.php/challenge-tell-me-about-yourself-so-i-know-how-i-can-help-you/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"181\">Take the challenge of introducing your self.</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Let\'s consider your development environment</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you are reading this you are probably far enough into web development that you have at least a starter machine and programs to get the work done.    I have a summary of development platforms that you should read to consider what you have, what you might need to move forward.   At the end of that I\'d like to know what you have and what you think you might need.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/index.php/development-platforms/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"175\">Learn more about development platforms..</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Take a challenge to <a href=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/index.php/challenge-tell-me-about-your-development-setup/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"184\">tell me about your current development setup...</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Software development freelancing activities</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>According to <a href=\"https://www.dictionary.com/browse/activity\\\">Dictionary.com an activity</a> is </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">the <strong>state</strong> or quality of <strong>being active</strong>:</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><em>There was not much activity in the stock market today. He doesn\'t have enough physical activity in his life.</em></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>a specific deed, action, function, or sphere of action</strong>:<em>social activities.</em></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>So, if you want to be a \"<strong>software\"</strong> \"<strong>development\"</strong> \"<strong>freelancer\"</strong> you need these kinds of activities:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Learning</strong>: gaining the knowledge to understand software.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Training</strong>: practicing, getting evaluated and coached.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Hiring</strong>: finding a job and establishing a contract.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Planning your work:</strong> figuring out how you are going to do the work, when, and reporting your plan.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Equiping</strong>: getting the tools and platforms needed.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Developing</strong>: building, completing, testing and documenting.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Delivering</strong>: handing it over to your client.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Getting paid</strong>: completing the contract, satisfying the client, and getting the pay you have earned.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Rinse and repeat.</strong></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You <strong>can\'t</strong> do these things by yourself!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>A <strong>learner</strong> needs a <strong>teacher</strong>.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>A <strong>trainee</strong> needs a trainer or <strong>mentor</strong>.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>A <strong>freelancer</strong> needs a <strong>client</strong> with a <strong>job</strong>.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>A <strong>planner</strong> needs many things:  decomposition, stages of work, planning, documenting, reviewing, coordinating...</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Equipping</strong> requires a <strong>source</strong> of tools, platforms, and process knowledge to be ready to do the job.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Developing</strong> is a whole process in itself, covered elsewhere on this site.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Delivery</strong> requires a <strong>repository</strong> to document your process and contain your deliverables so they can be used by the client or others.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Getting paid</strong> requires coordination with the client, an escrow agent, a funds transfer agent, and your bank.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Rinse and repeat</strong> requires <strong>learning</strong> from one job and the <strong>courage</strong> and <strong>determination</strong> to start all over again. </li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>You can do this!</strong>  This site will lead you to all of these things and you can be a success. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The internet to the rescue!</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>So, where do you find all of these people and things?  There are web based platforms that can supply all of these.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Teaching platforms</strong>: Wikipedia, the WWW, <strong>this site somewhat.</strong></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Training platforms</strong>: FrontendMentor, CodingBootCamp?, <strong>this site</strong>!, Discord, Slack.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Freelancing platforms</strong>: Upwork.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Planning platforms</strong>: Agile alliance, ?</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Equipping platforms</strong>: Google Play, AppStore, Linux \'apt get\', homebrew, many commercial sites. </li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Development platforms</strong>: GitHub, GitLab, Jira, Gerrit ?</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Delivery platforms</strong>: GitHub, GitLab, AppStore, Google Play.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Payment platforms</strong>: Upwork, Payoneer, your bank, mobile apps.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Encouragement platforms</strong>: <strong>this site! </strong></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Finding work as an individual</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>There are a number of <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Freelancer\">freelance</a> marketplaces online.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://www.upwork.com/freelance-jobs/\">Upwork</a> is one we recommend.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/index.php/finding-work/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"79\">Learn more about freelancing work...</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Working as part of a team</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Because of the rapid pace of technology development and market requirements, most web and application development is done by integrated teams.  No one person can do it all themselves. It takes a team of specialists working individually and cross discipline to be successful. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A team can take on big jobs that a single person cannot do.   This presents opportunity for the individual developer.  Once you understand how a team can work together you can find the best place to contribute.   But while you are doing what you already know how to do, you will also learn something about the rest of the team and the roles they fill.   And you will find avenues to learn new skills while you build team skills.   </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/index.php/working-in-a-professional-team/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"149\">Learn more about working as part of a larger team ...</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Development platforms</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Doing web development work as an individual can be done with most any computer running Windows, Linux, or Macintosh.   You most likely already made a choice and are doing work.   However, as you move into full stack work, or start working as part of a team it will get more complex.   It is worth considering the options again. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>So, take a moment to<a href=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/index.php/development-platforms/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"175\"> learn more about development platforms...</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Accepting challenges to put your learning to work.</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You may have already encountered a prompt to accept a challenge as you have read this far.  If so, good for you.   I will continue to add more challenges to keep you moving forward.  </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Learn more from the <a href=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/index.php/take-a-challenge/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"178\">complete list of challenges...</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How to do many things related to this work</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I continue to develop <a href=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/index.php/how-to/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"108\">how to pages on simple and more advanced topics.</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Latest Posts</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:latest-posts {\"align\":\"center\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For a full list of posts, visit the <strong><a href=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/index.php/blog/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"449\">Blog page</a></strong>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->','Home','','inherit','closed','closed','','2-revision-v1','','','2024-06-28 22:38:31','2024-06-28 22:38:31','',2,'https://michaelkentburns.com/?p=488',0,'revision','',0),
(489,1,'2024-06-28 22:39:56','2024-06-28 22:39:56','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I use this blog to announce new content as well as tell stories about my students and what they are learning and doing.  </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Latest Blog','','inherit','closed','closed','','449-revision-v1','','','2024-06-28 22:39:56','2024-06-28 22:39:56','',449,'https://michaelkentburns.com/?p=489',0,'revision','',0),
(490,1,'2024-06-28 22:40:54','2024-06-28 22:40:54','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I use this blog to announce new content as well as tell stories about my students and what they are learning and doing.  </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Latest Blog Posts','','inherit','closed','closed','','449-revision-v1','','','2024-06-28 22:40:54','2024-06-28 22:40:54','',449,'https://michaelkentburns.com/?p=490',0,'revision','',0),
(492,1,'2024-06-29 18:19:13','2024-06-29 18:19:13','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Michael lives near Cedar Park, Texas with his wife Mary.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"layout\":{\"type\":\"flex\",\"flexWrap\":\"nowrap\",\"justifyContent\":\"space-between\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":39,\"width\":\"309px\",\"height\":\"auto\",\"aspectRatio\":\"1.3360655737704918\",\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/IMG_1613-1024x768.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-39\" style=\"aspect-ratio:1.3360655737704918;width:309px;height:auto\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":169,\"width\":\"324px\",\"height\":\"auto\",\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/MichaelAtWork-1024x768.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-169\" style=\"width:324px;height:auto\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Michael is a 40 year veteran software engineer.  The last 33 years was as a principal systems developer at <a href=\"http://www.sas.com\">SAS Institute</a>.  His main responsibility was the <a href=\"https://www.sas.com/en_us/search.html?q=metadata%20server\">enterprise metadata server</a> that connects all SAS products. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>He is now happily retired, but not yet done with the field.  This site is home base for his new focus of mentoring programmers in the art of software engineering.   The main emphasis is individuals living in a places that do not have software development jobs.  This means that their best opportunity is to go freelance.   Doing so allows them to stay in their culture and home community.   </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>While freelancing is a start, there are also opportunities to do so much more as part of a larger development team focused on many open source software projects.   This is something that I am moving into myself.  Join me.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Students and Contributors</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Using the power of the internet and all the collaborative software available, I can now mentor and collaborate with like minded individuals around the globe. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Bukavu, Democratic Republic of the Congo </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>My first cohort of students live in the city of <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bukavu\">Bukavu</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">Cohort-1</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cohort-1 contains three guys that I met during my first visit to Congo in May 2023: </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Click here to see the Cohort-1 page for more details. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:gallery {\"linkTo\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":353,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/work-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-353\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Philémon</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":397,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ash-picture-1024x875.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-397\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Ashuza </figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":358,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Efatha.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-358\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Efatha</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></figure>\n<!-- /wp:gallery -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":1,\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\"></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">Cohort-2</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Contributors</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I am grateful to those who have read this site and made valuable contributions through feedback and contributed material. <a href=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/index.php/about-michael/contributors/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"295\">See this full list.</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:social-links -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-social-links\"><!-- wp:social-link {\"url\":\"https://github.com/MichaelKentBurns\",\"service\":\"github\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:social-link {\"url\":\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/michaelkentburns/?lipi=urn%3Ali%3Apage%3Ad_flagship3_feed%3B6Dj3E8auRSy51Ad%2BgA7N%2FQ%3D%3D\",\"service\":\"linkedin\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:social-link {\"url\":\"MichaelKentBurns@gmail.com\",\"service\":\"mail\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:social-link {\"url\":\"https://www.facebook.com/michael.burns.906\",\"service\":\"facebook\"} /--></ul>\n<!-- /wp:social-links -->\n\n<!-- wp:social-links -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-social-links\"></ul>\n<!-- /wp:social-links -->','About us','','inherit','closed','closed','','22-revision-v1','','','2024-06-29 18:19:13','2024-06-29 18:19:13','',22,'https://michaelkentburns.com/?p=492',0,'revision','',0),
(494,1,'2024-06-29 20:01:16','2024-06-29 20:01:16','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I met these three guys during my first visit to Congo in May 2023.  I chose them for Cohort-1 because they were already well prepared and they are a good mix of technical abilities and experiences. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Jean Bahati Philemon</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":353,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/work-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-353\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Philémon</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I first had contact with Philémon about in 2022 when he was getting started on Upwork.  He is a true pioneer in this field.   I gave him some recommendations about what international clients will expect to see when evaluating web developers.  One of my recommendations was to get a GitHub account and start posting his work.  He jumped right on that and took off.   He not only has a 100% job success rating, but is also Top Rated.  When you see the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://support.upwork.com/hc/en-us/articles/211068468-Top-Rated\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Top Rated</a>&nbsp;badge on an Upwork profile, it means that person is considered to be in the top 10% of all Upwork users.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Not only is he a pioneer, he is also a leader and mentor. He spends a fair amount of time encouraging and advising others who wish to follow in his footsteps.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>His contributions to this site are shown on his <a href=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/index.php/about-michael/contributors/philemons-contributions/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"294\">contributions page.</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Philémon says: \"I am a Frontend Web Developer with 5+ years of experience in developing websites. I have a passion for creating user-friendly, visually appealing, and functional websites. My expertise lies in HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript, React js, Tailwind, and Bootstrap. I have a strong understanding of web standards and accessibility guidelines.\"</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Github: <a href=\"https://github.com/bahati7\">https://github.com/bahati7</a><br>Upwork: <a href=\"https://www.upwork.com/freelancers/~01f54e6da3d373b5f2\">https://www.upwork.com/freelancers/~01f54e6da3d373b5f2</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Ashuza Destin</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":397,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ash-picture-1024x875.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-397\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Ashuza </figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hello! I’m&nbsp;<strong>ASHUZA Destin</strong>, a tech enthusiast with a particular passion for development, especially in applications and websites. I’m primarily focused on backend development, specializing in the PHP programming language, particularly with the Laravel framework. However, I also have some knowledge in frontend development, including HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and Bootstrap.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/AshDest\">GitHub: https://github.com/AshDest</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Upwork: <a href=\"https://www.upwork.com/freelancers/~01c7a3ec16524a8602\">https://www.upwork.com/freelancers/~01c7a3ec16524a860</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ash has wide experience in full stack development and does excellent work.   <a href=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/index.php/about-michael/contributors/ashuza-destins-contributions/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"317\">His contributions page </a>for this site shows that he has made major editing and development of several of the pages.   </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Efatha Byamungu Rutakaza </h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":496,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/IMG_2344-768x1024.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-496\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Efatha</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Efatha is the least experienced of this group, but he more than makes up for that by being a very eager and enthusiastic student and worker.   He has learned some important aspects of working as part of a team, and others are wise to learn from him.   </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\"Staying updated, leveraging, networking, and follow all of the instructions.\"</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\"Clear and consistent communication is essential, and realized that collaboration is far more productive than competition...\"    \"When team members support each other and share knowledge freely it creates a positive and productive work environment.\"</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:embed {\"url\":\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/971718809?badge=0\\u0026autopause=0\\u0026player_id=0\\u0026app_id=58479\",\"type\":\"video\",\"providerNameSlug\":\"vimeo\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-vimeo wp-block-embed-vimeo\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\nhttps://player.vimeo.com/video/971718809?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479\n</div><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><a href=\"https://www.upwork.com/freelancers/~013a3c69f58b323c60\">Interview produced by Théophile Achiza</a></figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:embed -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Efatha says: \"I am an experienced Front-End Web Developer with a strong background in HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Bootstrap. I specialize in creating responsive, modern web templates, visually appealing websites and applications. Skilful in Figma for designing user-friendly interfaces, I bring a comprehensive approach to aesthetic excellence. Let\'s collaborate to bring your vision to life!\"</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Upwork: <a href=\"https://www.upwork.com/freelancers/~01f4543035bc52ff94\">https://www.upwork.com/freelancers/~01f4543035bc52ff94</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>GitHub: <a href=\"https://github.com/efatha/\">https://github.com/efatha/</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Their work together</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>These three have collaborated on a full stack solution that presents a selection of question/answer surveys.  Once completed and submitted, the results are written out in JSON file format and submitted to a backend server where the data is written to SQL tables.   The survey results can then be queried from the database and viewed.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You can try their demo on our demo server: <a href=\"https://demo.MichaelKentBurns.com\">https://demo.MichaelKentBurns.com</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>More important than the finished product is the code and process they used to build the demo.  You can view all that in the <a href=\"https://github.com/MichaelKentBurns/MKB-cohort-1-Demo\">GitHub repository they used to do the work.</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Cohort-1','','publish','closed','closed','','cohort-1','','','2024-07-11 17:38:50','2024-07-11 17:38:50','',0,'https://michaelkentburns.com/?page_id=494',0,'page','',0),
(495,1,'2024-06-29 18:26:04','2024-06-29 18:26:04','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Michael lives near Cedar Park, Texas with his wife Mary.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"layout\":{\"type\":\"flex\",\"flexWrap\":\"nowrap\",\"justifyContent\":\"space-between\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":39,\"width\":\"309px\",\"height\":\"auto\",\"aspectRatio\":\"1.3360655737704918\",\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/IMG_1613-1024x768.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-39\" style=\"aspect-ratio:1.3360655737704918;width:309px;height:auto\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":169,\"width\":\"324px\",\"height\":\"auto\",\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/MichaelAtWork-1024x768.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-169\" style=\"width:324px;height:auto\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Michael is a 40 year veteran software engineer.  The last 33 years was as a principal systems developer at <a href=\"http://www.sas.com\">SAS Institute</a>.  His main responsibility was the <a href=\"https://www.sas.com/en_us/search.html?q=metadata%20server\">enterprise metadata server</a> that connects all SAS products. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>He is now happily retired, but not yet done with the field.  This site is home base for his new focus of mentoring programmers in the art of software engineering.   The main emphasis is individuals living in a places that do not have software development jobs.  This means that their best opportunity is to go freelance.   Doing so allows them to stay in their culture and home community.   </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>While freelancing is a start, there are also opportunities to do so much more as part of a larger development team focused on many open source software projects.   This is something that I am moving into myself.  Join me.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Students and Contributors</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Using the power of the internet and all the collaborative software available, I can now mentor and collaborate with like minded individuals around the globe. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Bukavu, Democratic Republic of the Congo </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>My first cohort of students live in the city of <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bukavu\">Bukavu</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">Cohort-1</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cohort-1 contains three guys that I met during my first visit to Congo in May 2023:  See details.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:gallery {\"linkTo\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":353,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/work-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-353\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Philémon</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":397,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ash-picture-1024x875.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-397\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Ashuza </figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":358,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Efatha.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-358\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Efatha</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></figure>\n<!-- /wp:gallery -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":1,\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\"></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">Cohort-2</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Contributors</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I am grateful to those who have read this site and made valuable contributions through feedback and contributed material. <a href=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/index.php/about-michael/contributors/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"295\">See this full list.</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:social-links -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-social-links\"><!-- wp:social-link {\"url\":\"https://github.com/MichaelKentBurns\",\"service\":\"github\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:social-link {\"url\":\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/michaelkentburns/?lipi=urn%3Ali%3Apage%3Ad_flagship3_feed%3B6Dj3E8auRSy51Ad%2BgA7N%2FQ%3D%3D\",\"service\":\"linkedin\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:social-link {\"url\":\"MichaelKentBurns@gmail.com\",\"service\":\"mail\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:social-link {\"url\":\"https://www.facebook.com/michael.burns.906\",\"service\":\"facebook\"} /--></ul>\n<!-- /wp:social-links -->\n\n<!-- wp:social-links -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-social-links\"></ul>\n<!-- /wp:social-links -->','About us','','inherit','closed','closed','','22-revision-v1','','','2024-06-29 18:26:04','2024-06-29 18:26:04','',22,'https://michaelkentburns.com/?p=495',0,'revision','',0),
